Package: RNewsflow
Type: Package
Title: Tools for analyzing content homogeneity and news diffusion using computational text analysis
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-02-14
Author: Kasper Welbers & Wouter van Atteveldt
Maintainer: Kasper Welbers <kasperwelbers@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of tools for tracing the flow of news messages over
    time and across media based on content analysis.
License: MIT
Depends: 
    plyr,
    reshape2,
    Matrix,
    tm,
    slam,
    igraph,
    scales,
    wordcloud,
    data.table
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
